The payload received on the rabbitMQ needs to be the following JSON
{â€œactionâ€:â€â€,â€sourceMailboxIDâ€:â€â€,â€sourceMessageIDâ€:â€â€,â€destinationMailboxIDâ€:â€â€,â€hashIDâ€,â€â€}
